cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.EM, cs.AR 

This paper deals with deep neural networks for image classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses optimizing the network for energy consumption, which is related to embedded systems (cs.EM). The use of classifiers of varying complexity is a form of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a principled optimization algorithm, which could fall under robotics (cs.RO) or computer architecture (cs.AR).
